snippet.textDisplay:
WOW this song has a potent statement regarding the disappearance of our cultures in favour of a shallow fast surface only politically correct lifestyle with a disregard for time honoured traditions that have great meaning, especially in religion or faith in ones God of their understanding... Traditions are great so long as they don't interfere with a persons evolution or spiritual & Intellectual growth as we are all on a different road of understanding & we need to respect individual freedom to pursue wellness & growth.
I enjoyed this song very much & it only served to remind me of those important life changing things I hold dear & tradition sometimes has gotten in the way of that pursuit but it also has shown me how tradition CAN & always does force people to maintain an old way that no longer has value or has a double meaning. 
Traditions are good as long as they motivate change spiritually & Intellectually to reinforce or moral center & intellectual growth.
I love watching foreign music videos to see how other people deal with life.
We need tradition to remain cohesive as a community Whether local or global
Thank you for this video, it sure gave me something to think about for the rest of my day :)
